Welcome to Perma-Fix Environmental Services
We are a global provider of safe, compliant, and environmentally responsible nuclear services and radioactive waste management solutions. We have built our company by developing solutions to our clients’ most challenging projects.  We are a certified small business under NAICS code 562910 Environmental Remediation (less than 750 employees).  We invite you to explore our offerings to help you with your next challenge.

Radioactive and Hazardous Materials Management
Nuclear Deactivation, Demolition and Remediation
Radiological and Industrial Hygiene Programs
Instrumentation Laboratory
Environmental Engineering

 
















