Instrumentation Services


About Us
Contact Us












Perma-Fix Instrumentation Services


        Perma-Fix has been providing the nuclear industry with quality instrumentation services since 1991.
      


        Perma-Fix provides rental, calibration and repair services for radiological and industrial 
	      hygiene instrumentation.  We are located in Knoxville, Tennessee and possess one of the country’s 
	      largest commercial instrument inventories.
      

        When results matter, Perma-Fix's rental, calibration and repair services are just an 
	      over-night shipment away.  Our Radiological and Industrial Hygiene instrumentation inventory 
	      is available for weekly or monthly rentals at affordable rates.
      
Custom and Specialty Instrumentation

        Perma-Fix offers professional consultation for custom instrumentation, application 
	      and development.  We also provide specialty instrumentation services that respond to 
	      today's nuclear industry including Decontamination & Demolition and environmental remediation
        support. Examples include:  ISOCS/LabSOCS, Gamma Spectroscopy and survey instrumentation coupled 
	      with Global Position Systems (GPS).  Perma-Fix can utilize radiological instrumentation 
	      together with GPS to produce precise field measurements on CAD-quality survey maps.
      
Instrument Calibrations

        Perma-Fix customers count on our quick response and quality work. All calibrations are performed to the 
	      requirements of ANSI N323A, 1997 unless otherwise requested.
      

        Perma-Fix Instrumentation Services (SEC*) operates under Tennessee Department of 
	      Environment and Conservation, Division of Radiological Health, Radioactive 
	      Material License numbers R-47161 and R-47209.
      

        To view all services and instruments including rental rates click here.
      

        *Safety and Ecology Corporation is a subsidiary of Perma-Fix Environmental Services, Inc.
      





