Perma-Fix Environmental Services, Inc.




 




8302 Dunwoody Place, Suite 250
                                                ,
Atlanta
                                                ,
GA
30350

USA

 
 
 


 
 

 
 
 


Companies
Perma-Fix Environmental Services, Inc.
 






Perma-Fix is an integrated nationwide network of treatment, storage and disposal facilities, transportation services, engineering consultants, site remediation teams, and government service centers that provides you with comprehensive, cost effective waste management services. The Company is based in Atlanta, Georgia. We have six major waste treatment and processing facilities across the United States. Perma-Fix has evolved over the years by developing unique treatment technologies and acquiring permitted waste treatment facilities. Presently, the company has three major business segments: Nuclear, Industrial and Engineering.

Company details


8302 Dunwoody Place, Suite 250
                                        ,
                                                                            Atlanta
                                        ,

                                            GA
30350
USA


More Office Locations
