Challenge Technology is the world leader in manufacturing and support of respirometric measuring equipment. For over 23 years, Challenge Technology has provided the highest quality respirometers available for testing in wastewater treatment and other fields, which use respirometry to gain an understanding of biological processes with respirometric evaluation.
 


                            based in Springdale, ARKANSAS (USA).
                        
 
 
 
 
 
 







 
 


